// _GENERIC_HOSTS guard, borrowed verbatim") + plan.md Task 1's explicit
// host list, which is a SUPERSET of vantage's own _GENERIC_HOSTS extended
// for this project's actual candidate pool: gitlab.com, netlify.app,
